{"tid":183972,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"整過容 你問我答","createTime":"2017-04-02T13:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T09:47:53.000Z","uid":22940,"like":12,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2502b647dd9353f8e24a90069da68c647d2c5517","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:18:03.000Z","msg":"抽脂  開眼頭 縫雙眼皮 <br />\n你問我答<br />\n自爆問題就不了"},{"pid":"31a7dea30c9bd3e55064aa61b8fdb31d1a3962f4","tid":183972,"uid":6957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"係邊到整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711924920580682fc973df260e4d27b181714dce","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係邊到整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台北"},{"pid":"16a50a4d1e0f1e0df4e45c78d52d688fce49b58f","tid":183972,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:22:38.000Z","msg":"有無副作用"},{"pid":"005c63a2e99bc4f11de71a3d805d30b17950f01f","tid":183972,"uid":60648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:23:23.000Z","msg":"整完生活有咩唔同<br />\n<br />\n點樣面對舊朋友"},{"pid":"18f70d99773055ad2f8226b7ae154758fb6e4ccf","tid":183972,"uid":22576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:24:34.000Z","msg":"抽脂抽邊？"},{"pid":"3fde7d9797823ea1b82e7c4fe6be3a1921270145","tid":183972,"uid":52066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:24:42.000Z","msg":"開眼頭同開眼尾邊樣風險比較大？"},{"pid":"1f6b94299e0e97018717f616b4ed74d19115a251","tid":183972,"uid":59979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"邊個醫生<br />\n一次過整哂定分開幾次"},{"pid":"14b7825b241a0c53bb8bd3373a9c4757579a7f75","tid":183972,"uid":58914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:25:05.000Z","msg":"整完個樣同心目中既樣同唔同"},{"pid":"02d0f3140b3e3a67524b79f1142b8985e9922ad3","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無副作用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暫時無副作用，老左唔知<br />\n開眼頭個位會有少少疤，但唔係好覺<br />\n合埋眼好自然 唔會覺得整過 因為唔係割 無痕"},{"pid":"a197b91e59648650a2648e6ee75615078d0c7aec","tid":183972,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:27:36.000Z","msg":"好容易睇得出整過<br />\n<br />\n我會恥笑佢地"},{"pid":"d5112c13e7db55f602a95302c6893dcb5d54c3ae","tid":183972,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:29:44.000Z","msg":"到二十尾就要大執<br />\n<br />\n好易發炎爛眼角<br />\n<br />\n易流眼女<br />\n<br />\n老左個樣會好怪<br />\n<br />\n通常要化粧遮刀口位<br />\n<br />\n自欺欺人"},{"pid":"37d7d85d5701ae2b30431237706e533b4214a698","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整完生活有咩唔同<br />\n<br />\n點樣面對舊朋友</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n整完生活其實無乜唔同<br />\n得到夢寐以求既一條眼摺<br />\n唔需要再為左眼摺痴膠紙<br />\n化妝無咁食眼線<br />\n<br />\n有同熟既朋友交待，佢地無乜野，反正整既又唔係佢<br />\n其他唔熟既無講，由得佢地發現講又好，無發現都好"},{"pid":"d4b945af5f5659392e7b280afa969ef87d6c4dba","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:31:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抽脂抽邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抽眼皮"},{"pid":"4cd3db4411fb83a027585985a8956f989e2e9cb4","tid":183972,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:32:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>整完生活有咩唔同<br />\n<br />\n點樣面對舊朋友</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n整完生活其實無乜唔同<br />\n得到夢寐以求既一條眼摺<br />\n唔需要再為左眼摺痴膠紙<br />\n化妝無咁食眼線<br />\n<br />\n有同熟既朋友交待，佢地無乜野，反正整既又唔係佢<br />\n其他唔熟既無講，由得佢地發現講又好，無發現都好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果我整容人d舊相會send比佢新識既人"},{"pid":"929c0fe177608bbc62f98ba9059e89142e098881","tid":183972,"uid":22576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"有無發覺多左人追"},{"pid":"668fa7253229c786f13aa149e80dc5e5af4f0c51","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:33:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開眼頭同開眼尾邊樣風險比較大？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該開眼尾 眼尾肌肉無力扯住<br />\n眼頭好多case都會開，通常係因為蒙古摺，開法都因應眼型有好多種"},{"pid":"ff3917036e664bbc767c32a5088b111ed1b30b3c","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:35:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個醫生<br />\n一次過整哂定分開幾次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台北最出名果幾位醫生 其中一位<br />\n隨便搵下都會知<br />\n一次過整，因為可以一次過恢復，但都可以分開。"},{"pid":"34ff8cec920fcb7557a89936f920a6e11b1a7076","tid":183972,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:37:50.000Z","msg":"醫生一定話你知無副作用<br />\n<br />\n因為要做生意"},{"pid":"652951577e570a8d9929ae8a387ee64dac8c149a","tid":183972,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:38:17.000Z","msg":"會有人做中介搵錢"},{"pid":"5096738df7847b63782ebc2bd589eee9b2ac7ac2","tid":183972,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:39:32.000Z","msg":"化妝要重手去遮刀紋<br />\n<br />\n唔化就好撚怪"},{"pid":"0c330437995776775a4d3ce25373194ad3c00561","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整完個樣同心目中既樣同唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老老實實有，原本隻眼偏韓，尖眼頭幼內雙<br />\n而家隻眼偏美，開眼頭外雙<br />\n係精神左，影相會好sharp，不過照鏡有時都唔覺得係自己<br />\n可能我覺得韓式雙眼皮靚D掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1572e9c4d838edea80ca57a7c1055c4f3edb286b","tid":183972,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:40:20.000Z","msg":"整左幾錢?"},{"pid":"cb6d047c725f2f7d55fbecf52dec78279006cb00","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:40:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好容易睇得出整過<br />\n<br />\n我會恥笑佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔識你，你笑唔到我"},{"pid":"de0700dc8444e6863b8f55ff469b1ea5fb96cbc7","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:41:22.000Z","msg":"[qu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ote]到二十尾就要大執<br />\n<br />\n好易發炎爛眼角<br />\n<br />\n易流眼女<br />\n<br />\n老左個樣會好怪<br />\n<br />\n通常要化粧遮刀口位<br />\n<br />\n自欺欺人[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n咁到時先再執啦<br />\n而家我都唔洗化裝遮刀口位 認真"},{"pid":"f0680c144a9248f0649a2469941a0817a0fc3e96","tid":183972,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好容易睇得出整過<br />\n<br />\n我會恥笑佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔識你，你笑唔到我</blockquote><br />\n你朋友會<br />\n<br />\n除非你整完就完全脫離之前識既所有人"},{"pid":"b58281b26ffa368444e8f438ee8e79d070f14e62","tid":183972,"uid":44286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:42:48.000Z","msg":"你姓蔡？"},{"pid":"6aacfbe3a9e161dec8773941ef79de152f28d823","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>整完生活有咩唔同<br />\n<br />\n點樣面對舊朋友</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n整完生活其實無乜唔同<br />\n得到夢寐以求既一條眼摺<br />\n唔需要再為左眼摺痴膠紙<br />\n化妝無咁食眼線<br />\n<br />\n有同熟既朋友交待，佢地無乜野，反正整既又唔係佢<br />\n其他唔熟既無講，由得佢地發現講又好，無發現都好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果我整容人d舊相會send比佢新識既人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後呢？因為一條眼摺 佢新識果個人就識左另一個人？"},{"pid":"430359bc7091fce257d3f9b327508794b1d1adb9","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:45:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無發覺多左人追</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無，唔係因為吸引人所以去整<br />\n整完都無特登去識男仔"},{"pid":"a402d4d3f679b6e0a68d21ba48cffffa73660c2e","tid":183972,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>整完生活有咩唔同<br />\n<br />\n點樣面對舊朋友</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n整完生活其實無乜唔同<br />\n得到夢寐以求既一條眼摺<br />\n唔需要再為左眼摺痴膠紙<br />\n化妝無咁食眼線<br />\n<br />\n有同熟既朋友交待，佢地無乜野，反正整既又唔係佢<br />\n其他唔熟既無講，由得佢地發現講又好，無發現都好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果我整容人d舊相會send比佢新識既人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後呢？因為一條眼摺 佢新識果個人就識左另一個人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女人最鐘意拎呢d野來笑"},{"pid":"ae1135e6281741c24d436bb184d3e93e7a458253","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫生一定話你知無副作用<br />\n<br />\n因為要做生意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己做得呢個決定<br />\n要take咩risk自己知<br />\n做手術一定有風險，但醫生既技術都好重要"},{"pid":"8d2f9e1253d305a9f576406aa54016d5dd86d021","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>化妝要重手去遮刀紋<br />\n<br />\n唔化就好撚怪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本來都唔係成日化眼妝既人<br />\n而家仲方便左，唔洗搞隻眼，化底妝出得街"},{"pid":"b304d1310479826bb2c159508eef529badfd9fc9","tid":183972,"uid":62842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:50:52.000Z","msg":"有冇圖睇？<br />\n<br />\n整左幾多錢？<br />\n<br />\n台灣既醫生質素好唔好？"},{"pid":"05bf68216e32ea1e8ae5ff2c3254ad17634c85b6","tid":183972,"uid":91605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:58:58.000Z","msg":"點抽眼皮脂肪，要幾耐recover?"},{"pid":"7856590ef4dd82e4925f88e5d28b174bf19aabf4","tid":183972,"uid":42908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:59:11.000Z","msg":"內雙應該開眼頭定割好？<br />\n<br />\n做左幾錢？"},{"pid":"1f2e9c430320fbc76e49c381331d98aedcfd4886","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整左幾錢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n準確價錢唔記得了<br />\n每個項目收費<br />\n縫眼皮<br />\n開眼頭<br />\n抽脂<br />\n全身麻醉<br />\n加埋好似兩萬五至三萬港幣，算貴"},{"pid":"d2ced5abedd22583e788bc2810f00ba906d8f545","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好容易睇得出整過<br />\n<br />\n我會恥笑佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔識你，你笑唔到我</blockquote><br />\n你朋友會<br />\n<br />\n除非你整完就完全脫離之前識既所有人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係我「朋友」就唔會<br />\n笑的話，佢地唔係我朋友。"},{"pid":"834b339812e13bdbe129991630dbeeebef5bbd60","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你姓蔡？</blockquote><br />\n自爆問題不了"},{"pid":"01cad436a625404d51681265a03fdf638905bbc2","tid":183972,"uid":85243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>整左幾錢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n準確價錢唔記得了<br />\n每個項目收費<br />\n縫眼皮<br />\n開眼頭<br />\n抽脂<br />\n全身麻醉<br />\n加埋好似兩萬五至三萬港幣，算貴</blockquote><br />\n差唔多啦 唔叫貴<br />\n除非你同大陸做既比姐"},{"pid":"6c4bf41e2e89c9396340b3b6ecbe1a7c352407aa","tid":183972,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"縫雙眼皮？ 係永久？"},{"pid":"f5f2603487e5704277c8bf31f5d3e3080b078778","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇圖睇？<br />\n<br />\n整左幾多錢？<br />\n<br />\n台灣既醫生質素好唔好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n類似咁啦，原本窄，而家高D 但又無張圖咁高<br />\n我就滿意我呢個醫生既。但台灣太多整型診所，質素實參差<br />\n價錢同埋多唔多客可以反映，呢種手術有少少工多藝熟"},{"pid":"4a4625973f4df2662b27fb595dca022ef9b488e1","tid":183972,"uid":79981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"有冇睱疵？"},{"pid":"b486a43e7f7d00e6a2d53e2b3c57b95caea2aeab","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點抽眼皮脂肪，要幾耐recover?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似係係眼皮上開個細窿拎D脂肪出黎，我抽左隻眼無咁泡，傷口唔知係邊<br />\nrecover 因人而異，創傷愈多愈耐 <br />\n例如割會耐過縫，開眼頭＋縫又耐過淨縫<br />\n我自己就一個月都仲少少怪咁，三個月正常好多"},{"pid":"34ac02ae721c6fb210b84c13752802e8dfae0a1d","tid":183972,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>整左幾錢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n準確價錢唔記得了<br />\n每個項目收費<br />\n縫眼皮<br />\n開眼頭<br />\n抽脂<br />\n全身麻醉<br />\n加埋好似兩萬五至三萬港幣，算貴</blockquote><br />\n點解要全身麻醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba87bd0d6070d1d44b5a1fc1405ef9ea3814791","tid":183972,"uid":83844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊個醫生<br />\n一次過整哂定分開幾次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台北最出名果幾位醫生 其中一位<br />\n隨便搵下都會知<br />\n一次過整，因為可以一次過恢復，但都可以分開。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個醫生貴姓？"},{"pid":"098822010ae97b83e87fc6384c5901a5dc87987e","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:25:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>內雙應該開眼頭定割好？<br />\n<br />\n做左幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要睇你想要咩效果<br />\n同埋原本隻眼蒙古摺有幾多 <br />\n內雙可以唔開眼頭，縫高少少都可以好自然同sharp d <br />\n始終開眼頭會改變眼型，眼神<br />\n大陸就興全割，永久，但有事就難調整"},{"pid":"8f530f094a7782d91a4ba0308c88a04ab09a9e3f","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>整左幾錢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n準確價錢唔記得了<br />\n每個項目收費<br />\n縫眼皮<br />\n開眼頭<br />\n抽脂<br />\n全身麻醉<br />\n加埋好似兩萬五至三萬港幣，算貴</blockquote><br />\n差唔多啦 唔叫貴<br />\n除非你同大陸做既比姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽人做過大陸一千蚊有交易<br />\n但真係唔好信，人地成功唔等終你都成功<br />\n好有多人貪平做完 好快就鬆左跌左要再做<br />\n又見過有人開眼頭 永久有明顯疤"},{"pid":"6064d8db04de008f52779266f3196e82ea4fc00c","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>縫雙眼皮？ 係永久？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話永久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為縫都有好多種方法，我諗佢呢隻縫法縫得深少少，相對hold耐D"},{"pid":"5e0b51fc095abcfa385ffc51bc2be33373516d3e","tid":183972,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>縫雙眼皮？ 係永久？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話永久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為縫都有好多種方法，我諗佢呢隻縫法縫得深少少，相對hold耐D</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原理係咩？ 同吊線有咩分別？"},{"pid":"ffa80e829b257050c77814ee4245430fd2ec8af7","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇睱疵？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有，眼頭好近睇會有少少白既疤 <br />\n以前條內雙線仲留左少少係到<br />\n個雙眼皮唔係完完全全一樣高度<br />\n因為原本我都有D高低眉"},{"pid":"2a0ab2c490d861ded7a2dacd362fee770ff8bf48","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>整左幾錢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n準確價錢唔記得了<br />\n每個項目收費<br />\n縫眼皮<br />\n開眼頭<br />\n抽脂<br />\n全身麻醉<br />\n加埋好似兩萬五至三萬港幣，算貴</blockquote><br />\n點解要全身麻醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我原本都想局部，因為我唔怕痛<br />\n但佢話局部隻眼會開合，影響手術精準度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5079a57de9667966b18d44b206a846c1a995fb8","tid":183972,"uid":68298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:47:21.000Z","msg":"淨係開頭頭開眼尾唔知又要幾錢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22864feedc73e90f041f517f686891b19b68273","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊個醫生<br />\n一次過整哂定分開幾次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台北最出名果幾位醫生 其中一位<br />\n隨便搵下都會知<br />\n一次過整，因為可以一次過恢復，但都可以分開。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個醫生貴姓？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔幫人賣廣告了"},{"pid":"ce258438b002bd248ba1d9178ca1531d4abef30e","tid":183972,"uid":33001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:49:51.000Z","msg":"鍾意食咩生果"},{"pid":"e88336ca8549b61b5c8ece3f49f24fa2b7f63bee","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>縫雙眼皮？ 係永久？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話永久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為縫都有好多種方法，我諗佢呢隻縫法縫得深少少，相對hold耐D</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原理係咩？ 同吊線有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcR2J-_6r37ZAm5bltLyI0FSUcRVhr1i4S1AfaeZYqAnqX1KKph9sQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcR2J-_6r37ZAm5bltLyI0FSUcRVhr1i4S1AfaeZYqAnqX1KKph9sQ&h=0d0ffc8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.manhattan.com.tw/upload/images/%E6%95%B4%E5%BD%A2%E5%A4%96%E7%A7%91/%E9%9B%99%E7%9C%BC%E7%9A%AE03.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.manhattan.com.tw%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F%25E6%2595%25B4%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%25A7%2591%2F%25E9%259B%2599%25E7%259C%25BC%25E7%259A%25AE03.gif&h=0c6851dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都唔係太清楚，我估係好似張圖既縫法同埋縫到幾深既分別"},{"pid":"a6b1d051d8166184cb1fb4d5b9e587f65848cf6d","tid":183972,"uid":22667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:51:22.000Z","msg":"係台灣整咁要係果邊留幾耐等拆線？<br />\n同埋你係幾歲整"},{"pid":"208b31d4f6427c12139cf9b13fdbbb65e346907d","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係開頭頭開眼尾唔知又要幾錢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開眼頭價錢同雙眼皮差唔多<br />\n開眼尾都應該一樣掛<br />\n正常無乜事醫生唔會叫你開眼頭／尾<br />\n風險大D"},{"pid":"dc1542ce57058074eeb75ca3244051450e6526a9","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍾意食咩生果</blockquote><br />\n呢條是咪自爆問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩生果都鐘意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054b4f2bf56837d16d42f1ee2ef70010aea1d57e","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:56:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係台灣整咁要係果邊留幾耐等拆線？<br />\n同埋你係幾歲整</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n7日拆線<br />\n2X歲頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ca598d23c3af37811a55a193d3f1e0eb81e59b","tid":183972,"uid":25126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:00:01.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺得自己好不孝？"},{"pid":"13e7bd8aad016f32002b6db334851c4865f67c30","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺唔覺得自己好不孝？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔覺，我好愛我母親<br />\n每日痴同唔洗再痴 我睇唔到有分別"},{"pid":"ad1389dcf2b5349149ae78f61aa3700be7eb2b37","tid":183972,"uid":47276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:04:07.000Z","msg":"自信心有增強?"},{"pid":"dd8f70bee2aabbc0d3bc83ec446e010a41e1702d","tid":183972,"uid":6797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:05:22.000Z","msg":"手術後要住幾耐先出得院？<br />\n同埋係咪有塊白布包住對眼唔知要幾多日先除得？"},{"pid":"e735b2d2ef818236ef937564bd117c822a051b24","tid":183972,"uid":33001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鍾意食咩生果</blockquote><br />\n呢條是咪自爆問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩生果都鐘意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人緣好唔好"},{"pid":"502b3c72df2128a4378ff5552b04560dbd8a6582","tid":183972,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:07:58.000Z","msg":"再投胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c577079ac5e6c12dbb10d17f226a7a46641826","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:09:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自信心有增強?</blockquote><br />\n點都會有既，但真係好少<br />\n原本都唔係自信心低既人"},{"pid":"f51ff7b96a38c4bc9ca88253871efefc5eac02a3","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>手術後要住幾耐先出得院？<br />\n同埋係咪有塊白布包住對眼唔知要幾多日先除得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n麻醉過後，冰敷一陣 <br />\n3/4個鐘已經可以走 <br />\n無白布，唔洗包<br />\n係好腫 同埋少少痛<br />\n唔可以洗面，要冰敷 定時清潔傷口"},{"pid":"4e54f3aabac49ccb6e6f1442c90587b9f681c3ec","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鍾意食咩生果</blockquote><br />\n呢條是咪自爆問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩生果都鐘意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人緣好唔好</blockquote><br />\n還好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772df9c1833c3fb9de65089a9544125f7e109729","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再投胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個眼摺不足以令我再投胎 改變命運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9733d4ebd127c5eb6016891c455ce07c6b48bace","tid":183972,"uid":25496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"我都係內雙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企人知唔知你整"},{"pid":"42e7d922a2aff929b4548b7c9dceda4e00b3e4b2","tid":183972,"uid":53011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:18:31.000Z","msg":"見到d大陸雞一式一樣 大雙眼皮 尖下爬 高鼻<br />\n但一睇就知出自東門醫生手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n絲打 你整完有無好整容樣？<br />\n我都想整 但想整得自然 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 仔 單眼皮"},{"pid":"3f823bef4c4defe0be7a3b7c6a8c818d5aad59a4","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係內雙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企人知唔知你整</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實內雙都唔係咁差姐，眼皮唔好太dum就ok <br />\n屋企人知，無反對"},{"pid":"112a20ab47601d947d4c905b9a1dbc6df325d977","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到d大陸雞一式一樣 大雙眼皮 尖下爬 高鼻<br />\n但一睇就知出自東門醫生手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n絲打 你整完有無好整容樣？<br />\n我都想整 但想整得自然 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 仔 單眼皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我希望我無啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸人鐘意做好高<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/bdc000230956e1cf3ce\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2Fbdc000230956e1cf3ce&h=5fe75d18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我無咁高<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.dyjrzx.com/uploads/allimg/141203/1-141203143542K9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dyjrzx.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F141203%2F1-141203143542K9.jpg&h=bf3c79ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋整容樣 要做combo先有，打埋鼻面下巴果D<br />\n打針果D其實應該多人做好多 <br />\n<br />\n如果想自然 最好就係跟番眼皮形狀做高少少 但好少好少 <br />\n類似呢種<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過你又想諗 整咁少整黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋始終無自然既人工野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27bd7495329344253e1363b2da4d706025163a29","tid":183972,"uid":14341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:38:30.000Z","msg":"我諗我同你同一間整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6de0356b8a375d163f09e3ebfbc83b0c442a3d","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:41:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗我同你同一間整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分享下，咩效果？滿意醫生手勢嗎？"},{"pid":"d70f2b5202932cbca2f921e9da75d832ce34b2b2","tid":183972,"uid":13873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"整完照鏡之後<br />\n會唔會覺得自己好似好陌生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad58cd2d08f0c59948088da31fbad5d5fa10452","tid":183972,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:44:42.000Z","msg":"咁介意外表,唔識欣賞同接受天生生成個樣走去易容咁唔成熟,幾多歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">最撚憎人整容,笑鳩整容西都唔會笑豬扒</span>"},{"pid":"7e6cf636265760b01c7bddad67ad16bc802fc490","tid":183972,"uid":85243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁介意外表,唔識欣賞同接受天生生成個樣走去易容咁唔成熟,幾多歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">最撚憎人整容,笑鳩整容西都唔會笑豬扒</span></blockquote><br />\n八卦一問,人地整容有咩影響到你,點解會咁嬲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4123054c760a4bd18205309cbf040505926ac71a","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整完照鏡之後<br />\n會唔會覺得自己好似好陌生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n整完一路消腫都一路變緊，變自然D<br />\n我諗其他人可能唔會<br />\n我自己會，多多少少陌生，眼神唔同左<br />\n但唔係真係巨變，所以可以接受"},{"pid":"fb58d9e7a0f552299216c4c1f536195ccac4c723","tid":183972,"uid":14341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我諗我同你同一間整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分享下，咩效果？滿意醫生手勢嗎？</blockquote><br />\n其實復原得幾快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我易腫就想約重整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又愈來愈多人讚 就好滿意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064dc205db2d75fd79dddc71eb0a926def35231a","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁介意外表,唔識欣賞同接受天生生成個樣走去易容咁唔成熟,幾多歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">最撚憎人整容,笑鳩整容西都唔會笑豬扒</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實個樣係我既，我想我個樣變成點都可以係一個成熟既決定<br />\n我反而開心我而家已經做左，唔洗再搞來搞去<br />\n<br />\n不過最弊係我整左你都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  通常你笑豬扒都未笑到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58aac8b2c602d72c8e80ee96f6f91bc0e8045688","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我諗我同你同一間整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分享下，咩效果？滿意醫生手勢嗎？</blockquote><br />\n其實復原得幾快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我易腫就想約重整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又愈來愈多人讚 就好滿意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n腫仲可以點重整？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己喜歡就好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ccff355eb6ef3e6d2d3b262c909a7bb045cc8d","tid":183972,"uid":58367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"整容樣好易認，特別係整眼皮<br />\n<br />\n老咗會變老妖怪，即係夏蕙姨嗰種，面形浮腫，對眼勁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be05054783fa068a95cdcd03e7fb7007295b0c78","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整容樣好易認，特別係整眼皮<br />\n<br />\n老咗會變老妖怪，即係夏蕙姨嗰種，面形浮腫，對眼勁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你出街認到 拍下我膊頭話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我無打面 點樣面形浮腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdec3ad865054e278545e79dc3f799de0842abec","tid":183972,"uid":80397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:22:27.000Z","msg":"整完對眼會唔會同個樣好唔夾?<br />\n姐係本身山根唔高 無理由會有對混血眼"},{"pid":"ad70db0e7cce504fea2832ba4a00f76b2921d859","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:32:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整完對眼會唔會同個樣好唔夾?<br />\n姐係本身山根唔高 無理由會有對混血眼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果再整高少少 可能1mm都已經唔夾<br />\n有時自己望望下都會想個鼻高D 夾番對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔想再整喇，而家都幾好 唔太違和就算啦<br />\n所以整雙眼皮個高度係無標準<br />\n最緊要係夾番五官，呢D好關個醫生審美觀事"},{"pid":"848b1416ac6fc06553885a229a93d596c34319e0","tid":183972,"uid":56900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"天生眼袋好黑眼圈有無得整"},{"pid":"11d6c4a80603b2bc1e2b186d48199340b40d1470","tid":183972,"uid":56900,"like":0,"dislike":0,