冇得食，梗係嬲。"},{"pid":"9779011f27d0341edc912720d88a152aac47300d","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天生眼袋好黑眼圈有無得整</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知你眼袋 臥蠶 定黑眼圈<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.miyanlife.com/timg/160222/1644046117-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.miyanlife.com%2Ftimg%2F160222%2F1644046117-1.jpg&h=a5e35971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n收眼袋手術<br />\n呢方面既技術就應該有既<br />\n因為好多上左年紀既女士都好喜歡做<br />\n但眼袋位做手術風險高，原理一樣，眼下面無肌肉吊住<br />\n唔想整 得閒按下摩，早D訓仲好啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adaf55f536066b7063ee317c312fd1ba5b22b4fc","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>整完對眼會唔會同個樣好唔夾?<br />\n姐係本身山根唔高 無理由會有對混血眼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果再整高少少 可能1mm都已經唔夾<br />\n有時自己望望下都會想個鼻高D 夾番對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔想再整喇，而家都幾好 唔太違和就算啦<br />\n所以整雙眼皮個高度係無標準<br />\n最緊要係夾番五官，呢D好關個醫生審美觀事</blockquote><br />\n千其唔好整鼻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該唔會了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49eee3fe47d0919f94d6389bb0faed1a5ba4c358","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:54:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>整容樣好易認，特別係整眼皮<br />\n<br />\n老咗會變老妖怪，即係夏蕙姨嗰種，面形浮腫，對眼勁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOn9, 你有冇機會老都唔知啦，仲諗老左之後點？活在當下啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都明白有人唔接受整容呢件事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46922b7381c5d2336552e9445163ac2ed2580401","tid":183972,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:55:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整一整對眼要幾個月先正常<br />\n點翻工？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得一個月唔太夠，三個月先比較正常<br />\nD過渡期都係化濃妝 帶眼鏡遮下<br />\n唔洗翻工果時整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1d4215080bd3508fbfe00b6a5ae58e948e77c2","tid":183972,"uid":92983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:58:34.000Z","msg":"削面係咪風險太高？"},{"pid":"c6185ca03f976bc01debb959695bd56956c4b5d6","tid":183972,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:58:36.000Z","msg":"天然雙眼皮 尤其大眼睛嘅雙眼皮 嗰眼皮摺痕好易睇得出㗎喎<br />\n<br />\n整過嘅好明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5611c4c5954bbeffe57084b757b5275ce47bb1fa","tid":183972,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整完對眼會唔會同個樣好唔夾?<br />\n姐係本身山根唔高 無理由會有對混血眼</blockquote><br />\n唔會<br />\n<br />\n識人純華人，眼睛俾人話似混血"},{"pid":"2f642851e4dafb9c82a50e86dc30d10011ba93d3","tid":183972,"uid":6047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:00:15.000Z","msg":"三年前整過<br />\n而家開始跌返落黎 諗住再整<br />\n不過整完冇人發現 好自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為唔係成日見到父母 佢地都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}